The movie contains one of the longest average shot lengths in any motion picture 145.7 s.

The famous opening shot of Bela Tarr's &quot;Satantango&quot; is done in a single take lasting seven minutes.

 It is of a herd of cows walking across an empty landscape as the camera pans from right to left. 

 A single long take approximately 4 hours into the movie lasts an incredible 10 min 14 s.

No action, no comedy, No music, extremely slow, not entertaining just cult, annoyingly depressive for most people I believe. I warned you!

You need a lot of patience with  this movie. Have a look at the sample before dl.


